          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "轰击我魂向我施刑，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我仍固执不悔；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "但你怜悯征服我心，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
